{
  "stem": "1858.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 416.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, when I came to camp I was allowed to bring my things, but, soon, they were taken away from us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I had a few pictures, a little album, with pictures of my girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we had to turn everything in, I decided that we should hide it someplace.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we went to the place-- to the toilet on that hill.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And above the toilet, there was like a board, just a board.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I suppose it was to support it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we threw all those-- my little pictures on top of there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Hoping that if we survive, and the pictures will survive, we will recover them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We went to the hill, on the hill to the toilet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We call the toilets-- we called it [NON-ENGLISH], which meant the holy mount.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We gave it a name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we recovered the few pictures and I have them until today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Those are school pictures.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That little locket, I hid it under the bed, you know, where the foot of the bed was resting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just pushed it there, you know, into a little hole, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't hang onto it all the time and hold it in my mouth forever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was just for that temporary one day, then it was like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I hid it and I have it until today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not easy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that I had at least-- that I was clever enough that time to keep this and not to turn it in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I was frightened to death there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But, somehow, I took a chance, though I didn't realize that if they would find it on me, I could have been killed for it too.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But you're not always reason when you're faced with something like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
